            "html": "<p>You can add styles to your email using the <code>&#x3C;style></code> element. These styles dicatate how your email will look. All your <code>&#x3C;style></code> elements should live inside the <code>&#x3C;head></code> of your email. To prevent HEML from modifying your CSS, add the <code>heml-ignore</code> attribute. <strong>Note that it will still be inlined.</strong> </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-xml\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">heml-ignore</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* HEML will not modify the CSS in here */</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"embedded-css\"><a href=\"#embedded-css\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Embedded CSS</h2>\n<p>By default your styles will be inlined. However, any media queries will not be inlined. It is important to note that if you inline your CSS any client-targeting CSS should be put in a style element with the <code>heml-embed</code> attribute.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-xml\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">heml-embed</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* I won't be inlined */</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* I will be inlined */</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"attributes\"><a href=\"#attributes\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Attributes</h2>\n<div class=\"attributes-table\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>heml-embed</strong>\n<small>\nboolean\n</small></td>\n<td>If present, the CSS will not be inlined.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
